INSERT INTO `assignments_reply` VALUES (228, 172, 'Assignment: Define teaching & learning. Enumerate the strategies that will enhance effective learning and enlist the conditions of learning. Enlist the roles of a teacher. What are the types of clinical teaching? Describe the educational objectives that c', 'Sir,\r\n       Assalamualikum. Here I am submitting my assignment as an attachment, for your review please.\r\n       Thanks.\r\n       Dr.A.E.Md.Abdul WASEY', '2018-03-30 05:43:49', 'upload/attachment/bf4c4717b3ab3f911a30454b3ba11d15.docx', '<p>Dear fellow.</p><p>Congratulation for your assignment work. Your assignment accepted.  your concept regarding <b>learning</b> demands further clarification. <span xss=removed>\'Learning is</span><span xss=removed> a\r\nprocess resulting in some modification\r\nrelatively permanent of the behavior, in the way of thinking, feeling and doing of the learner. \'Learning is a c</span><span xss=removed>onstructive and active process that result in change in behavior\'. eg a learner can do that can not did beforehand.</span></p><p><font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span xss=removed>Try to apply the principles of learning & teaching in your professional life. Give emphasis to identify- learning situation,learning conditions,Learning skills.</span></font></p><p><font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span xss=removed>Thanks</span></font></p><p><font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span xss=removed>Prof Md Shah Alam</span></font></p><p><font face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span xss=removed>MBBS,DTCD, MCPS, MMEd</span></font></p><p><span xss=removed><br></span></p>', NULL, '2018-03-30 23:23:45', 'F');
