egy-5: Independent group work<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Strategy-6: Learning by doing (experiment)<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Strategy-7: Developing learning\r\nskills<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Strategy-8: Project works<o></o></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Strategy-9: Fine tuning</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><o><br></o></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><span xss=removed>wish your goodluck.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><span xss=removed>Prof Md Shah Alam</span></font></p></li></ol></ol></ol></ol>', NULL, '2018-04-03 22:57:46', 'F');
