INSERT INTO `assignments_reply` VALUES (245, 197, 'Assignment of M3 U 2 1. You are assigned to organize a daylong workshop on Medical education for 20 participants. a. Prepare a pre-workshop plan b. How will you run the workshop( Write Schedule) c. Write your plan of post workshop evaluation meeting.', 'Sir, \r\n       Assalamualikum. Here I am submitting my assignment as attachment for your review please.\r\n       Thanks.\r\n        Dr.Md. Abdul Wasey', '2018-04-06 05:50:10', 'upload/attachment/c35bd8f915c3ccebcf6fbcb02197e6a3.docx', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Dear fellow<o></o></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thanks for your assignment works. Your assignment works accepted.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Assignment: <u xss=removed>Prepare\r\na pre-workshop plan</u>, <b><u>Write  program schedule</u> & <u>Post workshop\r\nplan</u></b>  for a daylong workshop\r\nprogram of 20 participants.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o></o></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Workshop is a meeting during which people come together with\r\nexperts to find solution. Essential features are active participation and work\r\n& learn from practical experience or discussion. Participants may have to\r\nplay the role of <u>organizer & participant,</u> or group leader &\r\nrapporteurs. The organizer of the workshop is generally there to be consulted\r\nby the participant & help them when necessary but they don’t give lecture\r\nor impose solution. There are provisions of plenary session and or discussion\r\nin small group with flexibility in time. Plenary session needed to pool result\r\nof discussion or to clarify for all participant or to introduce some activity\r\nthat need unanimous approval. The success will depend largely on the way it is\r\nplanned & arrangement made before the opening session. Unless start working\r\nat least six month beforehand , increasing chance of  failure. Greater flexibility, adaptability of\r\nequipment & staff , and care for the need of participant must be looked\r\nfor.<o></o></p><