INSERT INTO `assignments_reply` VALUES (251, 202, 'Organization of a Day-long Workshop on Medical Education for 20 Participants ', 'You are assigned to organize a day-long workshop on medical education for 20 participants \r\na) Prepare a pre workshop plan\r\nb) How will you run the workshop (write schedule)\r\nc) Write your plan of post workshop evaluation meeting \r\n\r\na) Pre workshop plan \r\n• Selection of facilitator\r\n Facilitator will determine expected outcome or set targets to participants.\r\n Develop clear plan and tactics on how to achieve them.\r\n• Selection of workshop plan or template\r\n• Targets to be achieved\r\n Objectives – at the end of the workshop the participants will be able to \r\ni) Understand principles of effective teaching and learning \r\nii) Become skilled in various teaching methods\r\niii) Knows the principles and methods of assessment\r\n• Identification of participants- 20 participants including medical teachers of various medical colleges of Dhaka City having different levels of seniority (Registrar to Professor)\r\n• Venue\r\n Conference room, Ibrahim Medical College, 6th April 2018. \r\n Facilities- comfortable room temperature, made free from distractions, well-lit \r\n Equipment- laptop, internet access, flipcharts, display screen\r\n• Other equipment- Glue, scissors, blue tack, paper clips, stapler, pen etc. \r\n• IT instruments are set, a trial run practiced \r\n• Sitting arrangement- Circle of five learners around a table, four as such\r\n• Layout of planned activities\r\n• Ground rules are written and displayed in a flip chart\r\n Appear in time in each session \r\n Stay on schedule \r\n Switch off cell phones during session \r\n Avoid side conversations\r\n One speaks at a time, should not interrupt others while speaking \r\n Active participation\r\n Agree to disagree- contribute to safe and non-judgmental environment\r\n Ask questions \r\n Give sincere feedback \r\n• Informing participants in advance what need to know before hand in the accompanying invitation letter\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\nb) Schedule\r\nTitle: Medical Education\r\nVenue: Conference room, Ibrahim Medical College\r\nDate and time: 6th April 2018, 09:00 am to 04:00 pm \r\nSl. No.  Topics Methodology Starting time  Ending time\r\n1.  Registration  Lobby 09:00 am 09:05 am \r\n2.  Speed sharing, ice-breaking Questions/discussions 09:05 am 09:30 am\r\n3.  Teaching-learning  Presentation  09:30 am  10:00 am \r\n4.  Health break 10:00 am  10:30 am \r\n5.  Learning by doing Practical  10:30 am 11:00 am\r\n6.  Effective feedback  Presentation  11:00 am 11:30 am\r\n7.  Assessment on pre-requisite learning  MCQ 11:30 am 12:00 pm\r\n8.  Bedside/lab teaching  Presentation  12:00 pm 12:30 pm\r\n9.  Small group teaching (snow ball, buzz, fishbowl)  Practical  12:30 pm 01:00 pm\r\n10.  Lunch break 01:00 pm 02:00 pm\r\n11.  Interactive lecture  Presentation  02:00 pm 02:30 pm\r\n12.  Principles of assessment  Presentation  02:30 pm 03:00 pm\r\n13.  Written assessment (snow ball, buzz) Practical  03:00 pm 03:30 pm\r\n14.  Valediction  With faculty 03:30 pm 03:50 pm\r\n15.  Commitment  Oral  03:50 pm 03:55 pm \r\n16.  Closing 03:55 pm 04:00 pm \r\n\r\nHandouts, materials, supplies- Self-assessment checklist, power-point presentations, handouts\r\nc) Post workshop evaluation meeting \r\nThe meeting will be arranged with the organizers of the workshop. \r\n• Venue- Conference room, Ibrahim Medical College on 6th April, 2018 from 4:30 to 5:30 pm \r\n• Participants- Organizers, facilitators \r\n• Agenda- \r\n Review of learners’ feedback and suggestion \r\n Workshop documentation\r\n Next steps for improvements of workshop in future \r\n Review of contents \r\n Assign appropriate facilitators\r\n Improving facility arrangement\r\n Ensuring adequate logistics \r\n Change of food vendor \r\n Plan next workshop \r\n Assess business value \r\n Adjustment of facilitation process \r\n• Assign and prepare draft meeting minutes \r\n• Circulation of draft meeting minutes for feedback by next week\r\n• Finalize meeting minutes and circulate by next two weeks \r\n• Workshop document is drafted and circulated for feedback \r\n• Finalize workshop report and print\r\n', '2018-04-07 12:10:53', 'upload/attachment/486a8edef3a499da5ec8e8fad0e45dbf.docx', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
